Headline: Rubix Cricket Carnival 2016
News Content: Rubix 2016 organized by the Academy of Design (AOD) concluded successfully on 24th of July 2016 at Havelock grounds.The event was brought to life by a variety of fun yet exciting activities as well as a line of amazing stalls.Photographers - Gayanga Wijesena | Shehan Milantha | Weemansa DiasPhotos Credit Goes to - LetMeKnow.lk
